<ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">guard</ENAMEX> combat and combat support <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">units</ENAMEX> should eliminate <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">the weekend</TIMEX> drills and
instead have a single, <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">one month annual</TIMEX> training (<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">AT</ENAMEX>). The benefits of this
