            Increase the number of
effective field training <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">days</TIMEX> from <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">seven</NUMEX> to <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">23</NUMEX>. This assumes that the number of
preparation and cleanup <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">days</TIMEX> could be kept the same.

