<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">personnel</ENAMEX> turnover. In a <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">12</NUMEX>-man <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">unit</ENAMEX>, about every <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">four months</TIMEX> we lost a person
(due to enlistment expiration) and gained a <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">person</ENAMEX>. There was no way to set up
a stable <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">team</ENAMEX> to build skills because we constantly had to train someone new in
