dependence of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">units</ENAMEX>. Since unit <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">members</ENAMEX> must go to weekend drills <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">every month</TIMEX>,
